    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>Thanks. Good read.</p>
<p>&gt; Testing other controller-supported games led to the harsh conclusion that most of the other games do not recognize the DS4 at all.</p>
<p>It probably suffers the same thing that a lot of gamepads do: no native support within the kernel. Broforce is probably one of those few cases where generic gamepads can be used.</p>

